## Information we collect

We do not require accounts and do not collect personal information directly. Like most websites, we use cookies and similar technologies through the following services:

- **Google Analytics** — anonymous usage statistics (pages visited, session duration, approximate location).
- **Google AdSense** — our advertising partner may use cookies to serve ads based on prior visits to this or other websites.

## Your choices

You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting [Google Ads Settings](https://adssettings.google.com). Most browsers also allow you to block or delete cookies.

## Third-party links

Articles may link to external sites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites.

